by nicolas-grekas at 2024-10-08T07:45:31Z

Renamed to `SameSiteCsrfTokenManager`.

The option is named `stateless_token_ids`:

```yaml
framework:
    csrf_protection:
        stateless_token_ids: [my_stateless_token_id]
```

